org.apache.xerces.parsers.SAXParser itself does have the right default (true), 
the problem comes invoking the parser through JAXP. Here is what I see in 
SAXParserImpl:

        // "namespaceAware" == SAX Namespaces feature
        // Note: there is a compatibility problem here with default values:
        // JAXP default is false while SAX 2 default is true!

So, I don't see how we could solve this problem.
